arations\nwhich display an excess of close in giant planets and brown dwarfs. Hence we\nsuggest that fragmentation triggered by a binary companion may contribute to\nthe formation of these substellar objects.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 6 Jan 2022 12:53:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-19"}
