rties such as the photoluminescence (PL)\nspectrum, defect-related radiative and non-radiative carrier capture cross\nsections, and recombination lifetime of non-equilibrium carriers.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 6 Jan 2022 14:52:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-23"}
